data.name: richTextBox1.Text
data.value:
The "Test AI by step" feature of Connect4Theory let You run a step by step match involving two AI players.
You have to select two AI players and then start the game, using the "Next" button the current player make his move. With the "Prev" button You can undo the last move.
The matches will be displayed on the board.

data.name: explainMultiGameBox.Text
data.value:
The "Streak Test AI" feature of Connect4Theory let You run a streak of matches involving two AI players.
You have to select two AI players and the number of matches to be played. The matches will not be displayed on the board but at the end of the streak the game staistics will be displayed.
